{
  "stem": "942.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But soon after that-- a week or 10 days-- the work was finished and we were back in camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, in fact, the camp was closed down, and the water was shut off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did not pipe any water into the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, food they didn't give us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the dead bodies were not-- you know, they were just piling up on the square.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the back of the barracks, in the latrines, you know, anybody that died in their bunk, you know, if somebody else wanted to take over the bunk, they were just dumped in the back of the barrack in the latrines.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were people like cord-wood, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Grotesque sights, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the square, there were mountains, you know, piling up and-- of dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was nobody doing anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was typhus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, we were infested with lice, and we were so filthy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had typhus like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I guess a couple weeks after all this-- this terrible ordeal, we are now at May the 6th, and I remember I was on this bunk and somebody that could still walk, he went out and he came back, and he says that there is a white flag flying on the tower near the gate on the guard tower.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and I could hear him say this, but I thought I was in a feverish dream or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somebody else went out and checked this and he said, yes, that's-- there is a white flag and all the German guards have left for the-- from the towers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I thought that this was something really serious, and I crawled out from my bunk.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
